title:Dialogue1
---
VEX: Day 72 of Rehabilitation Project E. 
VEX: The system is capable of turning on. The unit can perform basic functions such as opening its eyes and nodding its head, but there is no ‘thought process’ behind its motions.
VEX: I’ve tried so many routing combinations with its internal circuitry, but I’m afraid this is a newer ASCO model which I’m not as familiar with...

